            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347zM12 0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12c0 2.136.558 4.14 1.535 5.878L.057 23.5l5.763-1.513A11.943 11.943 0 0012 24c6.627 0 12-5.373 12-12S18.627 0 12 0zm0 21.894a9.893 9.893 0 01-5.032-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.981.999-3.648-.235-.374A9.86 9.86 0 012.106 12C2.106 6.58 6.58 2.106 12 2.106c5.419 0 9.894 4.474 9.894 9.894 0 5.419-4.475 9.894-9.894 9.894z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="option-title">WhatsApp</div>
            <div class="option-sub">Respondemos al instante</div>
          </div>
          <div class="option-arrow">→</div>
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:hola@webripple.com.ar" class="contact-option email">
          <div class="option-icon">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="option-title">Email</div>
            <div class="option-sub">hola@webripple.com.ar</div>
          </div>
          <div class="option-arrow">→</div>
        </a>
        <a href="https://instagram.com/webripple" target="_blank" class="contact-option ig">
          <div class="option-icon">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1112.63 8 4 4 0 0116 11.37z"/><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="option-title">Instagram</div>
            <div class="option-sub">@webripple</div>
          </div>
          <div class="option-arrow">→</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-right">
      <div class="trust-box">
        <h3>¿Por qué elegirnos?</h3>
        <div class="trust-items">
          <div class="trust-item">
            <div class="trust-icon">⚡</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Entrega en 48 horas</strong>
              <span>Sin esperas interminables. Tu web, cuando la necesitás.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-item">
            <div class="trust-icon">🎨</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Diseño 100% a medida</strong>
              <span>Nada de templates genéricos. Tu marca, tu estilo.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-item">
            <div class="trust-icon">💰</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Precios accesibles</strong>
              <span>Calidad profesional sin pagar precio de agencia.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-item">
            <div class="trust-icon">🛡️</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Satisfacción garantizada</strong>
              <span>Si no quedás conforme, devolvemos tu dinero.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <div class="footer-brand">
      <div class="footer-logo">
        <svg width="28" height="22" viewBox="0 0 36 28" fill="none">
          <path d="M2 4L10 22L18 8L26 22L34 4" stroke="url(#fg)" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <defs><linearGradient id="fg" x1="2" y1="4" x2="34" y2="22"><stop stop-color="#0b7fcf"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#29c6e0"/></linearGradient></defs>
        </svg>
        <span>WebRipple</span>
      </div>
      <p>Páginas web profesionales para<br/>emprendimientos y PyMEs argentinas.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-links">
      <div class="footer-col">
        <div class="footer-col-title">Servicios</div>
        <a href="#servicios">Landing Pages</a>
        <a href="#servicios">Web Institucional</a>
        <a href="#servicios">Tiendas Online</a>
        <a href="#servicios">SEO Local</a>
        <a href="#servicios">Mantenimiento</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <div class="footer-col-title">Empresa</div>
        <a href="#portfolio">Portfolio</a>
        <a href="#precios">Precios</a>
        <a href="#contacto">Contacto</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <div class="footer-col-title">Contacto</div>
        <a href="https://wa.me/5491112345678" target="_blank">WhatsApp</a>
        <a href="mailto:hola@webripple.com.ar">Email</a>
        <a href="https://instagram.com/webripple" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-bottom">
    <span>© 2025 WebRipple · Hecho con 💙 en Argentina</span>
    <span>Aceptamos Mercado Pago · Transferencia · Cuotas</span>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
/* CONTACT */
.contact { padding: 100px 32px; background: white; }
.contact-inner {
  max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 80px; align-items: center;
}
.contact-title {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
  font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy);
  line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.contact-title em {
  font-style: italic;
  background: var(--grad);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
}
.contact-desc { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 40px; }
.contact-options { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
.contact-option {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
  padding: 18px 20px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 14px;
  transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  color: var(--text);
}
.contact-option:hover { transform: translateX(4px); }
.contact-option.wa:hover { border-color: #22c55e; background: #f0fdf4; }
.contact-option.email:hover { border-color: var(--blue); background: var(--off); }
.contact-option.ig:hover { border-color: #e1306c; background: #fff0f5; }
.option-icon {
  width: 44px; height: 44px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  background: var(--off); flex-shrink: 0;
  color: var(--blue);
}
.wa .option-icon { background: #f0fdf4; color: #22c55e; }
.ig .option-icon { background: #fff0f5; color: #e1306c; }
.option-title { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--navy); }
.option-sub { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; }
.option-arrow { margin-left: auto; color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.1rem; }
.trust-box {
  background: var(--off);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 20px; padding: 36px;
}
.trust-box h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 28px; }
.trust-items { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
.trust-item { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start; }
.trust-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
.trust-item strong { display: block; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 4px; }
.trust-item span { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }

/* FOOTER */
.footer { background: var(--navy); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
.footer-inner {
  max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 64px 32px 40px;
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 2fr;
  gap: 64px;
}
.footer-logo {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: white;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.footer-brand p { font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.7; }
.footer-links { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 32px; }
.footer-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
.footer-col-title { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: white; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.footer-col a { font-size: 0.85rem; transition: color 0.2s; }
.footer-col a:hover { color: var(--cyan); }
.footer-bottom {
  max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 20px 32px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px;
}
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .contact-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
  .footer-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
}
@media (max-width: 580px) {
  .contact { padding: 70px 20px; }
  .footer-links { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
}
</style>
